872	+//!
873	+//! | offset | field                  | direction |
874	+//! |--------|------------------------|-----------|
875	+//! |  0..4  | parent endpoint (i32)  | in        |
876	+//! |  4..8  | child proc nr (i32)    | in        |
877	+//! |  0..4  | child endpoint (i32)   | out       |
